{"tid":1578343,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"叉雞飯呀叔間鋪比人攻擊","createTime":"2019-09-18T05:58:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T15:35:57.000Z","uid":105037,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"6596fe42ec2c1f1085bd44ce111fb9a5e67271b9","tid":1578343,"uid":105037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:58:37.000Z","msg":"話說十五號個日叉雞飯呀叔撚完狗之後，隨即被一眾有心之人在網上去佢有份投資嘅日本雜貨店Facebook page進行攻擊，而且連同佢嘅屋企人都一同被起底。<br />\n<br />\n之後店主出咗一篇聲明：<br />\n對於本專頁突然收到大量攻擊性留言，我地有幾點要澄清﹕<br />\n<br />\n1. 我地留意到部份留言提及一位男子，並張貼其姓名及相片。現嚴正聲明該名人士與本店及公司毫無關聯。<br />\n<br />\n2.現任店主是於香港居住超過30年，識講廣東話的日本人，一直落心落力為街坊提供最優質的日本食品及服務，有口皆碑，從無對港人做出失禮舉措。若本店出現無禮款待的情況，店主誠心道歉。而對於因與本店無關人士而引起對我們的若干指責，我們懇請諸位收回惡意言論，為努力經營的店主留一個情面。如情況持續，公司將不得不作出進一步行動。<br />\n<br />\n3.我地正在準備重新營業，請關注我地既專頁，如有最新消息將馬上通知大家！<br />\n<br />\n世良田紀子小姐<br />\n<br />\n道之駅<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/michinoekiHK/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FmichinoekiHK%2F&d=Ii72mHdDrz30Fn2z87Evj%2FsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=945f09d8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/michinoekiHK/</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4hFVrtU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4hFVrtU.png&h=c3c941f3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03b6a6060e0cfb4a332931a6673dc3d9aba6edca","tid":1578343,"uid":105037,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T05:59:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"80f1e729f92d5f20ccdb90a78c8539d50d80f4f4","tid":1578343,"uid":50040,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:00:23.000Z","msg":"推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cfa03105c8787ed99b79bad48d9aef28c67823","tid":1578343,"uid":309045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-18T06:03:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"